 We feel that the additional complexity of using natural language as a way
 of describing emotions in computational frameworks will be challenging,
 but will offer insight into problems that continue to vex the field of
 affective computing as well as other tasks where descriptions are subjective
 and established through language, such as deriving behavioral analytics
 for clinical assessment.
 
